3.2.1處理內文用的涵式

FreqProcess <- function(file){
  Gossip <-  tbl_df(read.table(file, row.names = 1))
  wordsFreq <- Gossip %>% 
    group_by(x) %>%
    count(x)
  Gossip <- 
    data.frame(word = wordsFreq$x, freq = wordsFreq$n) %>%
    arrange(desc(freq))
  Gossip <- 
    mutate(Gossip, booleng = str_detect(string = Gossip$word, pattern = "[[:lower:]]")) %>%
    mutate(boolNum = str_detect(string = Gossip$word, pattern = "\\d")) %>%
    mutate(boolEng = str_detect(string = Gossip$word, pattern = "[[:upper:]]")) %>%
    filter(boolEng == FALSE) %>%
    filter(booleng == FALSE) %>%
    filter(boolNum == FALSE) %>%
    slice(1:30)
  Gossip <- 
    data.frame(word = Gossip$word, freq = Gossip$freq) %>%
    arrange(desc(freq))
  return(Gossip)
}

3.2.3:處理內文

M <- FreqProcess(Main)
Ti <- FreqProcess(Title)
AM <- FreqProcess(AskMain)
NM <- FreqProcess(NewsMain)
SM <- FreqProcess(ScoopMain)
FM <- FreqProcess(FBMain)
ATi <- FreqProcess(AskTitle)
NTi <- FreqProcess(NewsTitle)
STi <- FreqProcess(ScoopTitle)
FTi <- FreqProcess(FBTitle)
